        <p class="teaser">
            The Scottish singer-songwriter has reached critical acclaim and been nominated for several awards - including BRITs and GRAMMYs - since the release of his chart-topping, debut album &#39;Divinely Uninspired to a Hellish Extent&#39;. He has also become a viral sensation thanks to his persona on his social media.
        </p>
    
    
        <p class="expanded">
            Real Name: Lewis Capaldi<br />Born: 7 October 1996<br />Birthplace: Glasgow, Scotland
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="toggle is-hidden" data-action="toggle"
           >
            View more
        </a>
    
</div>

        

    
</div>

            
                <div class="

cardset
level1




">

    
